               <birth notBefore="1933" notAfter="1934">He was born at <placeName ref="LOC3577Gondar"/> between <date>1933-1934</date> . </birth>
                  
                  
               <floruit notBefore="1959"  notAfter="1987"> He was a prominent Amharic writer. He received his elementary education
                  in <placeName ref="LOC3577Gondar"/>, then graduated from <placeName ref="LOC1216AddisA"/> Technical School in <date>1956/57</date> 
                  specializing in radio mechanics. 
                  But he left his field of specialization and turned to journalism, made swift progress from a curb reporter up to the editor in chief until <date>1966/67</date>. 
                  He authored novels and plays. </floruit>
               <death  when="1987"> He died at <placeName ref="LOC1216AddisA"/> in <date>1987</date>.</death>
                  
                  
